title: LIVE: Auctioning Matt's DeLorean
description: This week Andrew Collins (@andr3wcollins) from Jalopnik joins us as Bring A Trailer auctions off Matt's DeLorean while we record the podcast. Additionally we review the new all-turbo non-turbo 911 lineup, Andrew shares his desert racing experience and his recent trip to Pikes Peak.
author: matt@thesmokingtire.com (Matt Farah & Zack Klapman)
